<div class="center-index-container">
  <div class="text-map-center">
    <div class="text-map">
      <div class="lorem-ipsum">
        <h1>Save a life be a hero</h1>
        <p>
By donating blood, you not only give a part of yourself but also offer hope to those in need. Every donation matters and can save lives in emergencies, during surgeries, and in the treatment of various health conditions. The process of blood donation is simple and safe, taking only a short amount of time to make a significant difference. Whether you're donating for the first time or a regular donor, your contribution is invaluable to those relying on blood transfusions for their survival. By donating blood, you're not just giving blood but also hope and a future to people in need.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="map-container">
        <div data-controller="map"
          style="height: 100%;"
          id='map'
          data-map-api-key-value="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>"
          data-controller="map"
          data-map-markers-value="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
          data-map-api-key-value="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="section-cards">
    <div class="title-center">
      <h2>Centers</h2>
      <p>Embrace the profound impact of donating blood. With each donation, you offer someone another chance at life. <br> Let your empathy flow freely, be the guiding light in a world that often feels dark. Donate blood, and witness the incredible power of empathy.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="center-index-cards">
        <% @centers.each do |center| %>
          <%= link_to(center_path(center)) do %>
            <div class="card-center">
              <p class="card__title"><%= center.name %></p>
              <p class="card__body"><%= center.address %></p>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
